{"tid":1546255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不追究或特赦涉事示威者有違法治嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T08:28:02.000Z","uid":301327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6be17b0e8c19c824bf2747afd7cc8928cc5b549b","tid":1546255,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:16.000Z","msg":"潘熙大狀已率先表態「要求不對示威者作出檢控是合理及具法律基礎，因律政司可基於公眾利益等因素行使酌情權不提控」<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190617/59724665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59724665&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=337b01b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59724665&h=c50831f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190617/59724665</a>。如果你認為潘大狀唔夠藍，大可參巧馮華健資深大律師所講「有人暴動或犯罪，點解唔硬性起訴？個答案就係（律政司）有酌情權，個酌情權點解成立？因為社會係需要呢樣嘢，如果所有嘢黑白處理，未必尋求到一個對社會最有利嘅平衡」<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714282&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=483190cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190627%2F20714282&h=e06c5839\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190627/20714282</a>。<br />\n<br />\n退一萬步，就算如曾鈺成認為「被捕的年輕示威者經審訊後，特首可考慮特赦」<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785579&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=44c47057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785579&h=e7d09220\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190703/59785579</a>，但檢控工作點可能由一個向被捕示威者道歉嘅律政司去處理？ 這是甚麼狗屁不通嘅法治？誠然李國能反對特赦，他強調每個人都受到法律約束。不過，他亦表明政府應該同意由法官領導獨立調查委員會調查近期嘅事件 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190710/20724948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F20724948&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=14d4fb73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F20724948&h=16805a17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190710/20724948</a>。試問法庭單靠控辯雙方陳詞作供又點識別警方在常規或程序以外嘅疏漏或缺失以作出公平裁决？德批難民庇護比黃台仰李東昇正好說明這種碎片化及以暴動和襲警等脫離背景嚴重控罪作出檢控已經受到國際社會嘅質疑。更直接令到香港法治同司法獨立嘅國際聲譽受到損害。<br />\n<br />\n不追究或特赦涉事者有違法治嗎？就以老翁「暴力」令太太歸天獲法庭當庭釋放一案為例，咁有違法治嗎？當大家都沒整件事嘅來龍去脈而得知他太太是位苦不堪言嘅長期病患，我都可以中聯辨主任上身去批評有違法治。"},{"pid":"b10953ffd316635917dca32f4bf31b2c949f9e87","tid":1546255,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b40c45adb8fa222aeba8fad23020f01a63ef55b","tid":1546255,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd275cfc8eb71822c1fa779aa9089dc8fac7d65d","tid":1546255,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a hr